---
import Container from "./Container.astro"
---

<div class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300" id="use-cases">
  <Container>
    <div class="mb-20 space-y-4 px-6 md:px-0">
      <h2 class="text-center text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 dark:text-white md:text-4xl">
        Real-World Use Cases
      </h2>
    </div>
    <div class="md:columns-2 lg:columns-3 gap-8 space-y-8">

      <div class="aspect-auto p-8 border border-gray-100 rounded-3xl bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 dark:border-gray-700 shadow-2xl shadow-gray-600/10 dark:shadow-none">
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <div>
            <h6 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-white">Document Authentication</h6>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-8">
          Notary platforms can use Tisura to ensure signed documents are verifiably authentic. Each file’s origin can be proven cryptographically, eliminating doubts or disputes.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="aspect-auto p-8 border border-gray-100 rounded-3xl bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 dark:border-gray-700 shadow-2xl shadow-gray-600/10 dark:shadow-none">
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <div>
            <h6 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-white">AI Content Verification</h6>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-8">
          Newsrooms and media outlets rely on Tisura to trace the source of AI-generated content. This ensures only verified assets get published, preserving editorial integrity.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="aspect-auto p-8 border border-gray-100 rounded-3xl bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 dark:border-gray-700 shadow-2xl shadow-gray-600/10 dark:shadow-none">
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <div>
            <h6 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-white">API Response Proof</h6>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-8">
          Financial data providers use Tisura to certify that API responses were delivered at a specific timestamp. This offers verifiable proof for compliance and audit purposes.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="aspect-auto p-8 border border-gray-100 rounded-3xl bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 dark:border-gray-700 shadow-2xl shadow-gray-600/10 dark:shadow-none">
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <div>
            <h6 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-white">HR Document Integrity</h6>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-8">
          HR platforms can verify that CVs and identification documents originated from the applicant’s device. Tisura prevents tampering and adds trust to hiring workflows.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="aspect-auto p-8 border border-gray-100 rounded-3xl bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 dark:border-gray-700 shadow-2xl shadow-gray-600/10 dark:shadow-none">
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <div>
            <h6 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-white">Crypto Airdrop Fairness</h6>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-8">
          Web3 projects leverage Tisura to prove eligibility logic and reward distribution in airdrops. This ensures transparency and fairness in on-chain growth campaigns.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="aspect-auto p-8 border border-gray-100 rounded-3xl bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 dark:border-gray-700 shadow-2xl shadow-gray-600/10 dark:shadow-none">
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <div>
            <h6 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-white">Legal Dispute Evidence</h6>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-8">
          In legal disputes, Tisura enables parties to prove the origin and timestamp of digital documents. This cryptographic traceability strengthens evidentiary claims.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </Container>
</div>
